NAME

  **demoanim** - test sprite subsystem


SYNOPSIS

    demoanim 

DESCRIPTION

    Will display a demonstrative animation, to test if the sprite
    system is working properly. If it is, the command should display
    a sprite that rapidly cycles through the letters A, B, and C.
    Will throw an error if given any arguments. Hit any key to exit 
    the process when running. 


SEE ALSO

    democurses, demomarkdown, demomousetouch